## Version 1.0
* Basic CLI TIC TAC TOE game using Classes, program runs in one file While I debug and fix current issues.

## Version 1.1
* Updated the program to show state of the board for every turn the player takes. 
* Added quality of life features such as replay method that calls once the initial game has decided on winner or draw.

## Version 1.2
* Refactored existing classes and relative methods into seperate files for easier code readability.
